data.description: This charming, like new home offers 3 bedrooms all on the second floor, 2 full baths, and a half bath on the main floor. The front porch has been enhanced with concrete, providing a welcoming entrance. Upon entering, you'll notice the upgraded flooring throughout the home, adding a touch of elegance to each room. You will also see the comfortable and inviting living room area that flows into your kitchen and dining. The master bedroom boasts a large bathroom complete with a walk-in closet, ensuring plenty of storage space for your personal belongings. The additional bedrooms are spacious and can easily accommodate various needs, whether it be a HomeOffice or a cozy guest room. Additionally, there is a wood deck that overlooks the scenic golf course, perfect for enjoying the outdoors or hosting gatherings with friends and family. Located in a desirable area, this home is surrounded by amenities such as shops, restaurants, and recreational facilities. Its central location allows for easy access to major highways. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make Cotton Creek your new home!
